HOTA IND MFG CO said unconsolidated sales
in June fell 0.34% to NT$212,780,000 from NT$213,500,000,
according to a statement filed to the  Taiwan Stock Exchange .  (Figures are in thousands of New Taiwan dollars)  =================================================================  6/2011           6/2010
Sales            212,780          213,500    
YOY%              -0.34%   -----------------Year-to-date-----------------
Sales           1,240,113        1,068,102   
YOY%              16.10% 
=================================================================
 